# [Interview #128: WH Signing Report - Br00se, Entry #39](https://www.theoryland.com/intvmain.php?i=128#39)

#### Br00se

By now I had worked up enough courage to actually ask him some questions. I went out the car to get my note pad and to step to the Subway Deli a few doors down to use the restroom. When I returned, he was gone.
